<div class="modal-header">
    <button class="close" data-dismiss="modal">
        ×</button>
    <h3>
        How To Get Azure Subscription ID</h3>
</div>
<div class="modal-body">
    <ol>
        <li>
            <p>
                Go to <a href="http://windows.azure.com"  target="_blank">http://windows.azure.com</a> and sign in.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>Click on hosted Services
                <br>
                <img border="0" width="195" height="271" src="/Content/img/help/image001.jpg" /></p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>Click on your Subscription that are displayed in the center pane<br>
                <img border="0" width="293" height="202" id="Picture 33" src="/Content/img/help/image007.jpg" /></p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>In the properties Window you will find your <b>Subscription ID</b> near the
                bottom<br>
                <img border="0" width="209" height="374" id="Picture 3" src="/Content/img/help/image008.jpg" /></p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>Highlight the Subscription ID number, right click and on the popup menu click
                <b>Copy</b><br>
                <img border="0" width="305" height="103" id="Picture 5" src="/Content/img/help/image009.png" /></p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>Paste this value back in the <b>Azure Config </b>page <b>Subscription Id
                </b>field<br>
                <img border="0" width="488" height="83" id="Picture 6" src="/Content/img/help/image010.png" /></p>
        </li>
    </ol>
</div>
